==== ENTRY 1 ====
HEADWORD: Incurrent
<hw>In*cur"rent</hw> <pr>(?)</pr>, <pos>a.</pos> <ety>[L.
<ets>incurrens</ets>, p. pr. <ets>incurere</ets>, <ets>incursum</ets>,
to run in; <ets>in-</ets> + <ets>currere</ets> to run.]</ety>
<fld>(Zool.)</fld> <def>Characterized by a current which flows inward;
<as>as, the <ex>incurrent</ex> orifice of lamellibranch
Mollusca</as>.</def>⟦br⟧
[<source>1913 Webster</source>]</p>

<p><ent>Incursion</ent>⟦br⟧
